        <br>
        <p>
            <ul>
                <li><b>CERTIFICATION</b> – Get certificate from Incandescence after the successful completion of your CA tenure.</li>
                <li><b>ORGANIZE EVENTS</b> – Get hands – on experience to organize events in your college and get a chance of becoming a part of organizing team of Incandescence. </li>
                <li><b>LEADERSHIP OPPORTUNITIES</b> – Get a chance to lead a team from your college to this 4-day extravaganza and participate in live events and competitions.</li>
                <li><b>PUBLICATION</b> – All the CA’s get a chance to get feature on our official Facebook and Instagram page of Incandescence. </li>
                <li><b>PERKS</b> - VIP passes, merchandise and branded Incandescence goodies, free accommodation, chance to meet celebrities and artists along with food coupons and other cashback coupons for top performers. </li>
            </ul>


        </p>
